reviewtext: I wanted to try these Video Tapes for a long time so finally I decided to spend all that money and ordered them and what do I get? ...TDK Ultimate Quality, light Blue and Green Box with a Yellow and Orange Color Stipe across...Wrong Item! Amazon also sell those Tapes for a lot less. When contacted the Seller this is what they said..."HURRICANE SANDY WIPE US OUT, PICKING UP THE PIECES SOMEWHERE ELSE, CAN YOU HOLD YOUR ORDER"What do you say to That? I told the Seller,...I feel very sorry and had no idea and to forget about the order! ...Since I never was able to try the Highly Rated Video Tapes, the ones they send me are just OK! ...Thank You D.D.
